<br />

<br />
Invaluable for solo charming, and awesome for pulling. Reasonably fast cast time, mana free and minimal aggro. If you have a bad warrior tanking though, you might want to pull with slow, to increase his aggro on first successful taunt, and reduce the damage to you if mob is going to hit you anyway.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=2212" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.elerion.net/pics/sjhosig.jpg" border="0" /></a><span style="font-style: italic"><span style="font-size: 9px; line-height: normal">
<br />
"Carrot Cake Soup is like the taste of watching girls make out. It has an extraordinary power that oscillates between gentle and overwhelming, between light and dark, between pleasure and more pleasure." - Penny Arcade</span></span></center></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
