BoT is the same setup except it would be Forlorn Deeds and Sleep</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Mezrin Kortex</span> 65 Coercer <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=605959" target="_blank" class="postlink">Profile</a>
